ChangeLogTag: Tue May 31 12:28:12 UTC 2005  Johnny Willemsen  <jwillemsen@remedy.nl>

        * tao/ORB_Core.{h,cpp,i}:
          Load the PolicyFactory Registry when needed

        * tao/PI_Client/PolicyFactory_Registry.h:
          Added svc conf macros

        * tao/PI_Client/PI_Client.{h,cpp}:
          New files with static initializer for static builds.

          The PolicyFactory_Registry is now loaded on demand when needed from the
          PI_Client library. In a static build the end user must include
          tao/PI_Client/PI_Client.h to pre load the PI stuff.

